{"tid":1705250,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日唔罷工既就係藍！","createTime":"2019-11-11T00:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T09:40:46.000Z","uid":251395,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"080d2b3493a01a5dc8fe2d620979b3932c21de04","tid":1705250,"uid":251395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:48:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仲等被罷工？？<br />\n依家係要令到d非黃絲被罷工呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ceb6302c28e28ecdc0d8fe1ab305a66d423489","tid":1705250,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4cHBEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4cHBEO.jpg&h=aaf225a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有冇人記得10月1<br />\n根本有第一次就會有第二次<br />\n有第二次就會有第三次<br />\n遲早當街當巷殺死人<br />\n啲狗都唔需要負任何責任<br />\n覺得唔關自己事嗰啲人幾時先會醒啊<br />\n仲有落車拆rb屌人阻住你返工嘅人<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒阿！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e02bc6e2cd679e414dea712f2a6b2660b1a027d7","tid":1705250,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">離中午癱瘓中環剩餘一個鐘，喺屋企就即刻出黎 喺街就快d搭車！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e6bca0e053b8d36b13a8d283656e2e118a647d56","tid":1705250,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:38:43.000Z","msg":"朝早班港豬們仲返工返學<br />\n路面可以rb<br />\n地底可以搭鐵<br />\n又可以引一大班港奴出來 認住佢地個偽善樣<br />\n一個經濟城市<br />\n阻止勞動力釋放係最能夠逼令政府跪底<br />\n佢地唔肯罷 真香港人就幫佢地罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點係 班港豬點都會受到懲罰<br />\n成功rb 阻到返工<br />\n班狗出來 更加阻到佢地<br />\n字係香港人贏 公就係港豬輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反 放左工先出動<br />\n其實迴響冇咁大<br />\n港豬會覺得事不關己<br />\n因為佢地眼中 沒有良知 只有利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁 我地就由利益入手<br />\n<br />\n我地要令港豬醒吖！<br />\n<br />\n早上抗爭 突破樽頸！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然長遠係成立工會 保護咁多打工仔既權利<br />\n<br />\n應承我 應承所有義士 突破樽頸啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最新進度 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F214&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=de35892e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/214</a><br />\n成立工會步驟 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F203&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=406e5124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/203</a><br />\n各行業Group list <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F186&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=e0590042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/186</a><br />\n⚠️短期目標⚠️<br />\n15/11前：三罷頻道要過5萬subscribe<br />\n22/11前：新四大工會過五千申請<br />\n29/11前：第二批新工會成立<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴"},{"pid":"b3b39934dc812db948cb6effea0965cc756007c6","tid":1705250,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"另外有車既和理非可唔可以幫手著死火？<br />\n有車幫手塞 事半功倍<br />\n另外手足記得快閃 唔好等有狗先走<br />\n<br />\n本來罷左工<br />\n見中環開波又出左去<br />\n最後返左公司攞物資<br />\n同老闆講罷多幾日 多謝老闆"},{"pid":"83cef8190046893c2f38b18b9d16b35bfc8670b6","tid":1705250,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"